  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE THE MISSISSIPPI ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE AND STEM EDUCATION INNOVATION ACT; TO AUTHORIZE THE USE OF ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE TO SUPPORT STEM INSTRUCTION IN PUBLIC SCHOOLS; TO CREATE PILOT PROGRAMS FOR AI-ASSISTED LEARNING, TEACHER SUPPORT, AND CAREER PATHWAYS; TO PROVIDE SAFEGUARDS FOR STUDENT DATA PRIVACY; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
